EYNWKxO9VQ4.title: Homemade GameBoy FlashCart with Arduino flash reader writer
EYNWKxO9VQ4.description:
These are my two Game boy flashcard prototype i use to test my code on real gameboy together with my also homemade Arduino programmer.

The first prototype uses a 4mBit flash chip from AMD with 8kb of SRAM, while the second one uses a 32mBit flash chip with 32kb of SRAM, that can actually handle all gameboy existent games :)

The second prototype provides a mechanical switch to eventually select up to 4 roms on the same flash chip, it is also capable of managing both PLCC and DIP memories

info at : www.insidecode.it

EaQWevFr5KI.title: MUSIC OF ITALY - Notte della Taranta 2009 Italian Tarantella by "Carlo de Pascali"
EaQWevFr5KI.description:
Music of Italy at the Notte della Taranta Festival 2009 (Night of the Tarantula festival of the Italian tarantella) at Galatina (Lecce) "CARLO DE PASCALI" called "CANAGLIA" performing a tarantella sound with his TAMBURELLO (Italian drums) a free style "Pizzica Pizzica". The pizzica music is a sister of the TARANTELLA, infact the Taranta and Tarantella have teh same origin and are very expression of the Italian Music coming from Salento, natural, beautiful and high quality music of the Taranta Festival 2009 and the "Italian Music" for more info: http://www.italianbusinessguide.com/

Notte della Taranta 2009 a Calimera (Lecce) "Italian Music" by "CANAGLIA" Carlo de Pascali che propone una free style ricerca con il suo TAMBURELLO come espressione della cultura musicale della tradizione Salentina e Italiana. Carlo de Pascali fa vibrare tutti a Galatina con la sua dimostrazione di Tamburello con un'interpretazione eccelente e tanta gente ballando al ritmo della pizzica pizzica (Music of Italy)

En Galatina (Lecce) el festival de la Notte della Taranta 2009 (Noche de la Tarantula, pariente cercano de la Tarantella Italiana) nos regala "Carlo de Pascali" con musica "Pizzica Pizzica" que es de la familia de la Tarantella Italiana como expresion natural de la musica tradicional Italiana de alto nivel desde la pizzica clasica del salento y que son parte de la cultura e la musica Italiana lanzando al mundo la "Italian music"

I57DdAXOW9E.title: 5 New Ways to Tone Up with a Jump Rope
I57DdAXOW9E.description:
Get $5 off your FabFitFun Summer Box using promo code COSMO5 at vip.fabfitfun.com

http://www.cosmobody.com

We’ve got a new way to use one of your favorite childhood toys.  Jumping rope is a great way to burn fat and tone up fast, so hop into this super fun workout that will totally change your lower body. 
 
Jump Rope: Stay light on your toes and keep your abs tight.  100 rotations
 
Overhead Squats: Fold the rope in half and bring it over your head.  Spread your feet apart, shift your weight onto your heels and squat. 12 reps
 
Jump Rope: 100 rotations
 
Overhead Alternating Forward Lunges: Fold the rope in half and bring it over your head.  Step your right leg forward into a lunge.  Step back together. Repeat on the left leg. 12 reps
 
Twisting Lunges: While in a lunge position, hold the doubled rope in front of you and twist your upper body to the right. Switch legs and repeat on the left side.  12 reps
 
Jump Rope: 100 rotations
 
Curtsies: Hold your doubled rope out in front of your body at chest level. Step your right leg back and to the left behind your body.  Bend your left knee into a curtsy while rotating your upper body to the left.  Step back to center. Stepping back with your right leg, repeat on the opposite side.  12 reps
 
Jump Rope: 100 rotations
 
Plié: Double your rope and hold it over your head. Take a wide stance, turn your toes out, and drop into a squat. Keeping your core tight, lean side to side to work our obliques. 12 reps

For more great workouts from Astrid Swan, go to CosmoBody.com to start your free trial today!

This full motion animation video shows how Capstone microturbines can be utilized in an industrial cogeneration or trigeneration (CHP or CCHP) configuration to replace existing steam boilers used in an industrial process, improving efficiency while simultaneously reducing operational costs.  

Visit our website to learn more: www.capstoneturbine.com

Capstone Turbine Corporation® is the world's leading producer of low-emission microturbine systems, and was first to market with commercially viable air bearing turbine technology. The company has shipped thousands of Capstone turbines to customers worldwide. These award-winning systems have logged millions of documented runtime operating hours.

Capstone is a member of the U.S. Environmental Protection Agency's Combined Heat and Power Partnership which is committed to improving the efficiency of the nation's energy infrastructure and reducing emissions of pollutants and greenhouse gases.

A UL-Certified ISO 9001:2008 and ISO 14001:2004 company, Capstone is headquartered in the Los Angeles area with sales and/or service centers in China, Mexico, Singapore, South America, the United Kingdom and the United States.

b1Gq5JrgjgI.description:
คุณเคยมั้ยเวลาเร่งด่วนแล้วเกิดเจอปัญหายางรั่ว ยางแบน
คุณเคยมั้ยที่ต้องมานั่งเปลี่ยนยางกลางสภาพแดดร้อนๆ
คุณเคยมั้ยที่ตื่นมาจะขับรถไปทำงานแล้วเจอยางแบนเพราะว่าไปทับตะปูมาตอนไหนก็ไม่รู้
คุณเคยมั้ยเวลาที่จะไปเที่ยวต่างจังหวัดแล้วต้องมาเสียเวลาจอดรอเช็คลมยางที่ปั๊ม

ให้ Airman แก้ปัญหาของคุณสิค่ะ

Airman คือ นวัตกรรมเครื่องปะยางฉุกเฉินอันดับหนึ่งของโลก
และยังมียอดขายอันดับหนึ่งในประเทศไทย เรา บริษัท ลิลนุช กรุ๊ป จำกัด ผู้นำเข้า Airman Thailand
ที่ได้รับลิขสิทธิ์การนำเข้าถูกต้องจากประเทศเยอรมนีแต่เพียงผู้เดียวในประเทศไทย
ภูมิใจที่จะเป็นผู้นำความปลอดภัยมาสู่คนที่คุณรักหรือคุณที่รักคุณ
เพียงแค่เสียบสายเข้ากับยางที่คุณต้องการให้เติมลม ( ในกรณียางรั่ว ไม่ต้องดึงตะปู หรือหาจุดที่รั่วนะคะ เสียบสายเข้าจุกยางได้เลยค่ะ )
และเสียบสายชาร์ทเข้ากับช่องจุดบุหรี่ กดปุ่ม power และรอให้ได้ลมยางตามความดันที่คุณต้องการ
แค่นี้รถคุณก็สามารถไปต่อได้อีก 300 กิโลเมตรโดยที่คุณไม่ต้องเสียเวลา
เสียอารมณ์ และเสียเหงื่อในการเปลี่ยนยางอะไหล่กลางแดดร้อนๆ

ละถ้ารถคุณไม่มียางอะไหล่ล่ะ 
Airman คือคำตอบที่ดีที่สุดค่ะ เพราะ Airman สามารถช่วยให้คุณไปได้ไกลกว่า 300 กิโลเมตร
โดยที่คุณจะไม่ต้องเสียเวลาเพื่อจอดหาที่เปลี่ยนยางอะไหล่ เพียงแค่คุณมี Airman ติดรถไว้
น้ำหนักก็เบาเพียงแค่ 1.2 กิโลกรัม ในขณะที่่ยางอะไหล่มีน้ำหนักมากถึง 25 กิโลกรัม
พก Airman ไว้ทั้งสะดวกอีกทั้งยังช่วยคุณประหยัดน้ำมันอีกด้วยค่ะ

Full Crew

Use the Axii Sign to force one opponent to kill another. Do this 20 times.

Kill 10 opponents by knocking them off somewhere high with the Aard Sign.

Environmentally Unfriendly

Kaer Morhen Trained
Perform 10 effective counterattacks in a row without getting hit or parrying.

Can't Touch This!
Kill 5 foes in a fight without taking damage (except for Toxicity) and without using the Quen Sign.

Kill at least 5 opponents in under 10 seconds.

Attack, counter, cast a Sign and throw a bomb (in any order) in under 4 seconds.

Destroy all monster nests in the Velen / Novigrad region, or in Skellige.

Bombardier
Collect the formulae for 6 different bomb types.

Bookworm
Read 30 books, journals or other documents.

Armed and Dangerous
Find and equip all the elements of one set of witcher gear.

Power Overwhelming
Have all possible Place of Power bonuses active at the same time.

Complete all fistfighting quests in Velen, Skellige and Novigrad.

Win all the horse races in the game.

Munchkin
Reach character development level 35.

Destroy 10 monster nests using bombs.

Fist of the South Star
Defeat an opponent in a fistfight without taking any damage.

Geralt and Friends

Play three hero cards in one round of gwent and win the match.

Fiend or Foe?
Complete the contract on Morvudd.

Ashes to Ashes
Complete the contract on Therazane.

The Doppler Effect
Resolve the doppler problem in Novigrad.

Even Odds
Kill 2 monsters you have a contract on without using Signs, potions, mutagens, oils or bombs.

Mutant
Fill all mutagen slots.

About ABC Galaxy
Meet Giggs & Hugg - two adorable friends, as they travel and explore the “ABC Galaxy”. In their special scrap-like spaceship. Giggs is a giggly alien girl, who’s the captain in charge, and First Mate Hugg is a big galactic creature that loves to hug. Along with their spaceship computer - Alpha Betty - they discover new letter planets, investigate each one & learn all about the different letters – recognizing their shape, the way they’re being pronounced and a few words that start with each of the letters. “ABC Galaxy” is a series for 2-3-year-old children, especially designed to be a child’s first introduction to the ABCs.
